# 💻 Introduction to GitHub - Student Project
---

Welcome! 👋  
This repository is part of my learning journey through the **Introduction to GitHub** course offered by **GitHub Education**, within the **GitHub Student Developer Pack**.

---

## 🎯 Purpose
This project was created to:
- Understand the fundamentals of **Git** and **GitHub**.
- Learn how to **create and manage repositories**.
- Practice using **branches, commits, merges, and pull requests**.
- Explore **collaborative workflows** in open-source development.
- Document projects effectively with **Markdown**.

---

## ⚙️ Tools & Technologies
- 🧠 **Git** – Version control system  
- 🌐 **GitHub** – Code hosting and collaboration platform  
- 📝 **Markdown** – Documentation and formatting  
- ☁️ **GitHub Codespaces** – Cloud-based development environment  

